cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with the problem of zero-shot learning in image classification, which is a subfield of computer vision.
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a deep generative model for zero-shot learning, which is a subfield of machine learning.
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with the problem of learning to predict classes not seen at training time, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence.
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper uses class attributes to represent each seen/unseen class, which is related to natural language processing and semantic representation.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image classification, which is a subfield of multimedia.
